{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "3a66ad57-922c-4e1f-9b8a-816623ecca0c", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/3a66ad57-922c-4e1f-9b8a-816623ecca0c@3.pkg/1772597484750/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597485126", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/3a66ad57-922c-4e1f-9b8a-816623ecca0c@3.pkg/1772597484750/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597485126"}, "identifier": "3a66ad57-922c-4e1f-9b8a-816623ecca0c", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>一审题干；二审设问；三审题肢。</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>①：中国“维护正义”“坚定做赋能型大国”体现对国际秩序的维护，故①符合题意；</p>\n\n<p>②：题干中未体现全球冲突，中国“作出重大历史贡献”“相互成就”表明中国推动全球共同发展，故②不符合题意；</p>\n\n<p>③：题干强调中国“捍卫和平”“同世界各国谱写双向奔赴”，体现中国积极参与维护世界和平，故③符合题意；</p>\n\n<p>④：“一带一路”的倡议者虽符合事实，但题干未直接提及“一带一路”相关内容，故④不符合题意；</p>\n\n<p>故本题选A。</p>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<p>（改编·2025·辽宁·中考真题）2025年是中国人民抗日战争暨世界反法西斯战争胜利80 周年。中国曾为捍卫和平、维护正义付出巨大民族牺牲，如今坚定做“赋能型大国”，推动全球治理完善，与各国共促发展，书写双向奔赴、相互成就的新篇章。表明中国是（&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;）</p>\n\n<p>①国际秩序的维护者</p>\n\n<p>②全球冲突的调解者</p>\n\n<p>③世界和平的建设者</p>\n\n<p>④“一带一路”的倡议者</p>\n", "title": "（改编·2025·辽宁·中考真题）2025年是中国人民抗日战争暨世界反法西斯战争胜利80 周年。中国曾为捍卫和平、维护正义付出巨大民族牺牲，如今坚定做“赋能型大国”，推动全球治理完善，与各国共促发展，书写双向奔赴、相互成就的新篇章。表明中国是（   ）①国际秩序的维护者②全球冲突的调解者③世界和平的建设者④“一带一路”的倡议者", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["A"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/3a66ad57-922c-4e1f-9b8a-816623ecca0c@3.pkg/item.json?v=1754820139415", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "choice_type": "character", "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>①③</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>①④</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>②③</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<p>②④</p>\n"}], "prompt": "<p>（改编·2025·辽宁·中考真题）2025年是中国人民抗日战争暨世界反法西斯战争胜利80 周年。中国曾为捍卫和平、维护正义付出巨大民族牺牲，如今坚定做“赋能型大国”，推动全球治理完善，与各国共促发展，书写双向奔赴、相互成就的新篇章。表明中国是（&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;）</p>\n\n<p>①国际秩序的维护者</p>\n\n<p>②全球冲突的调解者</p>\n\n<p>③世界和平的建设者</p>\n\n<p>④“一带一路”的倡议者</p>\n", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878"}, "source": {"container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "tags": ["$M002000000", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "ff8080814371757b014390fcdce504bd", "44bec0c6-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "$RE0000", "$M003002000", "5036342749", "$RE0200", "6a74973a-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "$RE0201", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "ff8080814371757b014390fcdce504bd", "44bec0c6-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "6a74973a-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5"], "status": "ONLINE", "is_publish": false, "id": "3a66ad57-922c-4e1f-9b8a-81662